00:00:01.104 --> 00:00:09.290
... is the principle of that
pulsating part, that power within us,

00:00:09.290 --> 00:00:14.170
which we have to feel, and
which pulsates in everything.

00:00:15.283 --> 00:00:19.500
It happens with Sahaja Yoga, no
doubt, that the Kundalini rises,

00:00:19.500 --> 00:00:30.801
but that is not the end of it, because human being
is the instrument in which this light is manifested.

00:00:30.845 --> 00:00:36.849
But once it is manifested it is not necessary
that it would be all the time burning properly.

00:00:36.879 --> 00:00:48.399
There is a possibility, mostly it is a
possibility, that the light can go out.

00:00:48.399 --> 00:00:53.385
If a wind upside is against it, then it can go out.

00:00:53.415 --> 00:01:00.215
It can also subside a little bit. It may come
out it may flicker, it may dwindle a little bit.

00:01:02.772 --> 00:01:15.064
Because human beings, as they are, they
have got into three complications.

00:01:17.103 --> 00:01:23.906
As soon as they become human beings these three complications start in them.

00:01:23.909 --> 00:01:33.117
And because of three, these three complications, one has to know that if you have to get out of that you have to break certain knots.

00:01:33.117 --> 00:01:41.899
They are called as granthis in the Sanskrit language — which are giving you this falsehood — is the vitathat (वितथता)

00:01:41.899 --> 00:01:47.055
Falsehood that we think that you see, “In
this world, after all everything is science,

00:01:47.097 --> 00:01:52.315
and everything is what we see and everything beyond…”
And all those sorts of things are really false

00:01:52.315 --> 00:01:55.785
because, unless and until you rise
into Reality, you believe in them.

00:01:55.785 --> 00:02:01.283
After all what is God? And what is all this
talk of religion? What is the talk of Christ?

00:02:01.303 --> 00:02:03.033
And what is the talk of all these things?

00:02:03.057 --> 00:02:13.638
So all these problems become sort of identified with you.
Absolutely you believe in the falsehood all the time.

00:02:13.638 --> 00:02:18.179
You are more concerned about the
falsehood than about the truth.

00:02:18.179 --> 00:02:24.457
Even if you are concerned about the truth,
when you are born with the seeker’s mind,

00:02:24.457 --> 00:02:27.537
then you try to seek and you try to
think of something that is beyond,

00:02:27.537 --> 00:02:29.247
you try to understand

00:02:29.247 --> 00:02:32.438
that there must be something
beyond and something must happen.

00:02:32.468 --> 00:02:36.388
But still, you see, you are bound

00:02:36.416 --> 00:02:40.726
by these three complications
in life, by which ...

00:02:40.789 --> 00:02:45.136
these three complications we
accept the world as it is.

00:02:45.153 --> 00:02:49.116
Because we do not know the Reality. The
problem is we do not know the Reality.

00:02:49.116 --> 00:02:55.636
Till we come inside the Reality, we
really do not know even what is Reality.

00:02:55.676 --> 00:03:02.936
What is the basic substance
of our being, how do we live,

00:03:02.977 --> 00:03:09.917
what is the subtle being, how do we live and what is our aim, what we have to fulfil?

00:03:09.917 --> 00:03:13.357
All these questions are very vague in our mind.

00:03:13.357 --> 00:03:17.921
Then we start seeking here and there, we go
round here and there and try to find out.

00:03:17.971 --> 00:03:24.051
We talk to people, we read books and especially
we go to books which are philosophical

00:03:24.077 --> 00:03:32.560
and try to find out about what
must be done about Reality.

00:03:32.565 --> 00:03:37.535
Why are we drawn towards this? Why are we not happy? Why do we feel dissatisfied in life?

00:03:37.581 --> 00:03:41.018
Why do we all the time
hanker after sometimes,

00:03:41.018 --> 00:03:47.231
something and we do not feel fulfilled within ourselves and, why don’t we understand the meaning of our own being?

00:03:47.261 --> 00:03:49.341
Why are we driven like this?

00:03:49.341 --> 00:03:51.141
All these questions come to us…

00:03:51.161 --> 00:03:52.361
Please come in!

00:03:52.361 --> 00:03:59.461
All these questions come to us
and we start seeking about it.

00:03:59.501 --> 00:04:05.480
And actually our priorities, before
we get into it, are so false

00:04:05.480 --> 00:04:07.871
because we do not know Reality.

00:04:07.877 --> 00:04:10.377
So I mean, it’s not your fault, itself,

00:04:10.377 --> 00:04:16.087
if you do not know Reality, and then naturally…For example, somebody, to catch the train itself is very important,

00:04:16.117 --> 00:04:19.439
then to go in time is very important,
then to get some money is important

00:04:19.439 --> 00:04:22.999
and to get to a house is important, and
then to have some children is important.

00:04:22.999 --> 00:04:27.169
All these things become very much
more important than they should be.

00:04:27.209 --> 00:04:31.241
While the main thing, that is to seek within yourself:

00:04:31.295 --> 00:04:35.055
the point of what are we to seek
and what is so important about it,

00:04:35.055 --> 00:04:38.145
that every scripture
has talked about this,

00:04:38.171 --> 00:04:42.019
that you must seek within yourself,
you must find out yourself who you are.

00:04:42.019 --> 00:04:46.100
What is the reason? Why all of
them have been so much stressing?

00:04:46.100 --> 00:04:51.140
So until you enter into it you will not know.

00:04:51.158 --> 00:04:56.054
It is such a vicious circle, because of these
three complications I was telling you about.

00:04:56.076 --> 00:05:03.016
Because if, as it is described, that your
Spirit is absolutely a detached personality,

00:05:03.016 --> 00:05:11.776
it’s a detached being; it is not contaminated by
anything. It is absolutely complete by itself.

00:05:11.811 --> 00:05:15.336
It is joy, it is bliss, it is the truth.

00:05:15.357 --> 00:05:17.027
And where are we then?

00:05:17.027 --> 00:05:23.577
Why are we in such a mood that we have something very important for us in our life,

00:05:23.587 --> 00:05:26.087
very special for us?

00:05:26.087 --> 00:05:32.857
We think that, “Oh, this must be done. I must
get myself insured! I must do these things.”

00:05:32.870 --> 00:05:38.617
Then why, if that Spirit is such a powerful
thing, then what is the complication?

00:05:38.617 --> 00:05:45.310
What are the complications we have and
how do we get rid of these complications?

00:05:45.341 --> 00:05:52.990
Through your evolution from the amoeba stage, you can say, even from the absolutely from the, we call it the jad, the dead,

00:05:52.975 --> 00:05:58.000
from the absolutely from the
material stage to this state,

00:05:58.000 --> 00:06:01.308
it has achieved quite a
lot of detachment in a way.

00:06:01.308 --> 00:06:07.246
The detachment has come in a way that
you understand that you are not the dead;

00:06:07.260 --> 00:06:11.520
no, you are not. That much at least
everybody knows, that you are not.

00:06:11.520 --> 00:06:13.690
There are so many things
you are identified with

00:06:13.690 --> 00:06:16.440
but at least you know
that you are not dead.

00:06:16.481 --> 00:06:23.000
With the growth of materialism and by
changing matter and its forms and all that,

00:06:23.000 --> 00:06:27.180
then you realise one more thing: that
matter doesn’t give us happiness.

00:06:27.180 --> 00:06:29.907
I mean many people through
evolution realise it:

00:06:29.911 --> 00:06:34.627
that matter is not the end of our lives
and it is not going to give us happiness.

00:06:34.640 --> 00:06:37.571
Then, in the subtler form,
when you evolve even more,

00:06:37.571 --> 00:06:43.740
then you go into the arts and
the beauty of the matter:

00:06:43.759 --> 00:06:49.349
then you start seeing little deeper
than what the matter means to you,

00:06:49.381 --> 00:06:57.931
and you start thinking about its beauty,
its forms, its combinations and its harmony.

00:06:57.928 --> 00:07:01.538
So the subtleties
about matter develop,

00:07:01.538 --> 00:07:05.838
up to a point, through your
rationality and understanding,

00:07:05.858 --> 00:07:13.058
that you realise that this is... this
art, also has its finite nature:

00:07:13.058 --> 00:07:15.278
I mean how far can you go with it?

00:07:15.278 --> 00:07:20.218
And even if you have art and you become an artist and you are aesthetically very rich…

00:07:20.238 --> 00:07:26.278
there are people who can be called as masters of art and those who are really aesthetically evolved people,

00:07:26.330 --> 00:07:30.658
but if you go and see their lives you get a shock you realise what kind of artists are these?

00:07:30.658 --> 00:07:36.398
I mean, they are producing art and beautiful things and nothing goes inside! They are very materialistic,

00:07:36.439 --> 00:07:41.878
they can be mad people or they can
be absolutely obnoxiously boring.

00:07:41.898 --> 00:07:47.888
So why is it that these artists, you see
those who are creating all this,

00:07:47.888 --> 00:07:53.898
supposed to be something which is joy-giving, are so boring themselves and nothing goes inside them!

00:07:53.898 --> 00:07:59.718
And apart from that they are so oppressive,
and so much sometimes can be very egoistical

00:07:59.718 --> 00:08:06.895
or can be very, very methodical or meticulous and they could be absolutely mathematical about things.

00:08:06.911 --> 00:08:11.136
You start understanding that they are
not that abstract, as they produce.

00:08:11.136 --> 00:08:15.296
You see, they give some ideas, some
projections they do, but they may not be so.

00:08:15.331 --> 00:08:16.846
So again you start thinking:

00:08:16.870 --> 00:08:21.125
how is it that this matter, which
has gone to this subtle state,

00:08:21.134 --> 00:08:23.585
which is called as art and artists,

00:08:23.608 --> 00:08:30.570
why is it that this matter has not anything
in it to offer us of that eternal value

00:08:30.587 --> 00:08:34.930
or of that nature which is promised
to us through our scriptures?

00:08:34.943 --> 00:08:39.030
So some people do at this point,

00:08:39.030 --> 00:08:46.813
definitely they step over, I would say,
or they just collapse on that point.

00:08:46.811 --> 00:08:50.161
In the sense then they think, “Oh,
then there is nothing like scriptures.

00:08:50.161 --> 00:08:55.361
It’s all a mess. It’s all wrong. There may
not be anything. It’s a tall story told to us.

00:08:55.381 --> 00:09:00.321
And there may not be any truth about it, that
there is all pervading power and there is this God

00:09:00.316 --> 00:09:02.557
and you can become one with
God. It cannot be true.

00:09:02.596 --> 00:09:07.507
After all you can see that there is
so much of poverty in this world,

00:09:07.541 --> 00:09:11.597
there is so much of pain in this world, people are so unhappy, how can there be a God

00:09:11.587 --> 00:09:14.027
Who can tolerate all this?”

00:09:14.040 --> 00:09:17.000
I get letters of that kind
many a times, you see,

00:09:17.056 --> 00:09:20.520
that, “How people are so unhappy
and they are this and that

00:09:20.544 --> 00:09:24.885
and then how can you talk of God?”

00:09:24.911 --> 00:09:28.235
So this is the one complication we have

00:09:28.235 --> 00:09:30.865
and this is the complication
comes in, because

00:09:30.889 --> 00:09:39.976
the Atma, the Spirit, is enveloped
by our attention into the matter;

00:09:39.992 --> 00:09:44.372
because the matter has risen, our
attention has come from matter,

00:09:44.374 --> 00:09:50.222
and it has risen up to a
point where there is a knot

00:09:50.226 --> 00:09:56.914
by which we cannot see the
Spirit but we see the matter.

00:09:56.932 --> 00:09:59.985
This knot, I mean there’s a
big controversy about names.

00:09:59.995 --> 00:10:04.985
I would not like you to confuse it but we
can say like that, this knot is the knot

00:10:05.005 --> 00:10:15.374
which is the knot between
the Spirit and the matter,

00:10:15.393 --> 00:10:21.358
which is called as jad-prakruti (जड
प्रकृति) in the Sanskrit language.

00:10:21.409 --> 00:10:25.859
This is the first knot which
is a very difficult knot.

00:10:25.909 --> 00:10:28.409
We think, “This jug is mine.”

00:10:28.409 --> 00:10:30.329
And we think, “This chair is mine.”

00:10:30.308 --> 00:10:33.989
Even if somebody offers you a
chair, “Come along sit here!”

00:10:34.021 --> 00:10:36.161
and the another person is sitting
little bit lower, she’ll say, “Oh,

00:10:36.182 --> 00:10:39.351
she has given her a
chair which is higher!”

00:10:39.368 --> 00:10:44.848
All kinds of complications human beings
have! You know, it’s very delicate they are.

00:10:44.877 --> 00:10:52.267
They are so foolishly, sometimes, identified with things, like supposing a person…if you go more and more in the politics now,

00:10:52.267 --> 00:10:55.627
there’s a prime minister and he thinks
that someone is sitting on a chair,

00:10:55.642 --> 00:11:01.067
and he thinks that somebody is going to occupy that chair, then you see, all kinds of funny things start in his mind

00:11:01.067 --> 00:11:06.107
and all kinds of complications start. And he
thinks that he’ll be dislodged from that chair

00:11:06.107 --> 00:11:10.487
by which he’s been a prime minister, so he
starts working out his own plans and things.

00:11:10.487 --> 00:11:12.987
I mean the priorities are so much changed!

00:11:12.987 --> 00:11:16.511
Then you will start, sort of what
you call, canvassing for him

00:11:16.519 --> 00:11:18.411
and everybody going
for an election,

00:11:18.411 --> 00:11:19.718
and everybody fighting.

00:11:19.718 --> 00:11:23.408
I mean, the whole world is a
madhouse at these things you see:

00:11:23.408 --> 00:11:27.558
how to achieve that chair, that position,
by which he can become the prime minister.

00:11:27.589 --> 00:11:29.842
And the other one doesn’t come.
The other side working it out

00:11:29.842 --> 00:11:34.809
and, you see, it is very ‘important’. But what is
he putting on the chair, is another dead stuff.

00:11:34.829 --> 00:11:37.329
You see one dead is adorned by another dead.

00:11:37.329 --> 00:11:43.147
He’s dead as far as so many things are
concerned which are thought as the truth,

00:11:43.163 --> 00:11:47.107
because he doesn’t know the truth. Now
supposing you make somebody as a high priest.

00:11:47.114 --> 00:11:49.154
Now he is a high priest on a chair.

00:11:49.155 --> 00:11:55.034
To me, I see one dead thing sitting
on another dead thing, that’s all.

00:11:55.054 --> 00:11:59.964
Because the chair doesn’t understand these things, the one
who’s put on the chair doesn’t understand anything either,

00:12:00.000 --> 00:12:03.027
because it hasn’t got the
awareness to see what is the truth.

00:12:03.027 --> 00:12:06.657
So what’s the use of doing
such a jocular thing?

00:12:06.684 --> 00:12:11.874
It’s really a joke, but people are very
serious about it indeed. Very serious things,

00:12:11.874 --> 00:12:16.224
absolutely, they do all kinds of things
for these elections. It’s so serious,

00:12:16.224 --> 00:12:19.004
but if you stand from this angle

00:12:19.004 --> 00:12:24.524
and you should see that you start looking at it and you say, “What’s this? I never expected. What’s all going on?”

00:12:24.524 --> 00:12:26.714
You see, it’s quite silly.

00:12:26.729 --> 00:12:30.861
But we have to accept it
because we have misidentified

00:12:30.861 --> 00:12:34.281
through this one granthi, or
you can call it this knot

00:12:34.317 --> 00:12:40.985
of the jadaprakruthi or what
you call as this matter.

00:12:41.001 --> 00:12:47.830
Now for a Sahaja Yogi it is essential to see how far he is identified with his jadaprakruthi.

00:12:47.877 --> 00:12:52.550
It’s very important to see how
far is he identified with his,

00:12:52.550 --> 00:13:01.219
what you call the attachment or
the covering of this deadening.

00:13:01.265 --> 00:13:05.689
All that is subconscious is, all
what you call conditioning, is done.

00:13:05.689 --> 00:13:08.499
Everything that is dead is dead.

00:13:08.532 --> 00:13:17.462
Whether it is your dead matter or a
dead thought, it’s just the same.

00:13:17.481 --> 00:13:23.301
And the more you hover on it. You see, there are silly people I have known: I mean they have come to me in their thing.

00:13:23.301 --> 00:13:28.341
You see, supposing a wife has died, say
about thirty-five years back. Alright?

00:13:28.361 --> 00:13:30.861
So he is here weeping and crying,

00:13:30.861 --> 00:13:35.581
writing poetry about her. She’s dead about twenty-five years back. She might have been reborn as a child somewhere

00:13:35.601 --> 00:13:38.391
or something like that. He can’t
marry her again, nothing of the kind,

00:13:38.406 --> 00:13:42.901
but he’s writing poetry about her, crying and
weeping. And he expects everybody to weep.

00:13:42.901 --> 00:13:46.011
There are people, I have seen, they
sit down and they just weep about it.

00:13:46.021 --> 00:13:55.181
They just play records and things, melancholy things and just wasting all their precious tears on something that is dead and finished.

00:13:55.181 --> 00:13:58.009
Now, there’s no need to weep about
it, but they’ll go on like that

00:13:58.009 --> 00:14:01.969
and they enjoy such a thing very much
and they appreciate it very much.

00:14:01.996 --> 00:14:06.986
It’s most surprising! But people go on
wasting their energy, they enjoy it in a way,

00:14:07.016 --> 00:14:12.886
the way it is written down, the
whole melancholy of singing their

00:14:12.914 --> 00:14:18.986
damaged experiences and
remembering them in your memory.

00:14:19.003 --> 00:14:25.543
Whatever was false, actually should become
nothing in your mind when you reach Reality.

00:14:25.543 --> 00:14:30.043
So the memory in a Sahaja Yogi

00:14:30.053 --> 00:14:34.463
is of no value, much value. Because
whatever he had, was in a dead condition.

00:14:34.483 --> 00:14:38.123
He was not sensitive to
All-pervading Power at that time.

00:14:38.149 --> 00:14:40.649
He was just dealing with dead stuff, you see.

00:14:40.649 --> 00:14:43.746
And that was what I was surprised
when many people told me

00:14:43.746 --> 00:14:48.426
that, “Mother, after becoming a Sahaja Yogi now we can’t read any more melancholy poets.”

00:14:48.449 --> 00:14:52.229
I said, “Thank God a lot of time
is now saved for meditation!”

00:14:52.229 --> 00:14:57.469
Otherwise imagine all of them coming
with very melancholy faces to me,

00:14:57.482 --> 00:15:00.712
and saying that, “Mother you
know, this poet has written…”

00:15:00.727 --> 00:15:04.107
Already there are bombardments of people
who read all kinds of books, that,

00:15:04.107 --> 00:15:08.407
“Why such a person should write like that? And why such a person should write like that?”

00:15:08.452 --> 00:15:12.317
In the same way they would say, why
is such a person like Lord Byron?

00:15:12.317 --> 00:15:13.722
I don’t even see
his face you see,

00:15:13.722 --> 00:15:17.652
when we pass that way! I say he’s
really melancholia personified!

00:15:17.682 --> 00:15:23.154
And he made everybody miserable himself! What was he crying about? I mean if you see his life: whom did he make happy?

00:15:23.154 --> 00:15:27.514
He made everyone happy, and was crying all
the time and still making everybody unhappy?

00:15:27.514 --> 00:15:33.244
So this kind of a person is there! All this
is dead and takes you towards the dead.

00:15:33.251 --> 00:15:38.403
So dead and dead things can
never give you happiness.

00:15:39.883 --> 00:15:43.561
On the contrary it gives you
habits, they give you habits.

00:15:43.561 --> 00:15:49.860
And these habits come to you like, say, you are habituated to sit on the chair, you cannot sit on the ground.

00:15:49.901 --> 00:15:53.051
Now if I tell the Sahaja Yogis they
must learn to sit on the ground

00:15:53.071 --> 00:15:56.270
they will immediately start that, “We must sit on the ground!” That’s not the point!

00:15:56.301 --> 00:15:59.849
What I am saying the habit the chair
has given should be got rid of.

00:15:59.844 --> 00:16:02.864
But for that you don’t waste your
energies, for heaven’s sake!

00:16:02.864 --> 00:16:08.194
Because if I say that then you shouldn’t try wasting your energy in getting rid of the habits that were there.

00:16:08.194 --> 00:16:14.620
On the contrary if you put your attention
to your Spirit, to what you have achieved,

00:16:14.630 --> 00:16:18.100
to where you are, gradually you’ll find
your habits will drop out like that.

00:16:18.114 --> 00:16:24.215
You have known that. We have had alcoholics with us here; terrible alcoholics who could not give up alcohol,

00:16:24.215 --> 00:16:25.544
and they have given up.

00:16:25.534 --> 00:16:29.354
We have had people who have taken drugs;
they have given up without any difficulties.

00:16:29.413 --> 00:16:35.679
Cigarettes they have given up. I mean there are also some higher vices and bigger vices also people have given up.

00:16:35.713 --> 00:16:39.399
And some vices which one cannot
mention, people have given up.

00:16:39.422 --> 00:16:43.123
So this happens when your
attention goes to your Spirit.

00:16:43.123 --> 00:16:47.033
And this is a very big
detachment that comes to you

00:16:47.052 --> 00:16:55.713
through your ascent, into that realm
where you feel the All-pervading.

00:16:55.733 --> 00:16:58.233
Means automatically
your detachment works.

00:16:58.233 --> 00:17:06.273
Means your attention has felt, definitely, that oneness with Reality. Otherwise why are you getting detached?

00:17:06.273 --> 00:17:11.473
And spontaneously it happens. Suddenly you’ve matured so much. Sahaja Yogis matured so fast.

00:17:11.473 --> 00:17:16.303
I mean it’s a jet-like maturity, I think. Because
when they rise nobody understands, you see.

00:17:16.303 --> 00:17:19.127
Whenever they say something people
say, “What are you talking about?”

00:17:19.127 --> 00:17:23.777
Because they are at such a different level that others just don’t understand what they are talking about,

00:17:23.793 --> 00:17:25.775
and they find it very
difficult to understand.

00:17:25.775 --> 00:17:30.723
Easiest thing, whatever they talk, the others say, “What, what are you saying about, we don’t follow?”

00:17:30.745 --> 00:17:35.313
So the attention when it enters
into that, your habits drop out.

00:17:35.313 --> 00:17:39.690
But for that it is essential that your
attention should be on your Spirit.

00:17:39.690 --> 00:17:46.273
Now what is the beauty of Spirit for a Sahaja Yogi? What does he get out of the Spirit? What is the manifestation of Spirit is?

00:17:46.273 --> 00:17:54.397
That when his attention is absolutely
one with the Atman, with the Spirit,

00:17:54.397 --> 00:18:00.767
then there is a manifestation of vibrations.
You start getting cool breeze in your hands.

00:18:00.777 --> 00:18:09.801
Now these vibrations are there from the very beginning of the matter, up to the vibrations where you come up to a human level.

00:18:09.828 --> 00:18:13.620
So you can call them, these are
like, electromagnetic vibrations.

00:18:13.620 --> 00:18:19.768
But when they go on improving. You see, in the
beginning, they just look like electromagnetic,

00:18:19.768 --> 00:18:23.202
then they look like more. There
is emotions in it, you see.

00:18:23.202 --> 00:18:28.060
Then you go little ahead, then you
find that these vibrations also act.

00:18:28.090 --> 00:18:31.440
These vibrations also
think, they also report.

00:18:31.468 --> 00:18:35.988
So, you see, gradually you will find
that with the growth of human being,

00:18:35.988 --> 00:18:37.328
as a human being from matter,

00:18:37.328 --> 00:18:42.298
these vibrations have also manifested
into different categories.

00:18:42.327 --> 00:18:46.712
To begin with, these vibrations are only
electromagnetic, you can say, in the matter.

00:18:46.712 --> 00:18:53.667
Say if you have Sulphur Dioxide as a molecule you will find sulphur and dioxide both are vibrating all the time like that.

00:18:53.693 --> 00:18:57.483
But when it goes on manifesting
more and more. That’s the basics,

00:18:57.482 --> 00:19:07.833
then gradually the manifestation of these higher things can be perceived through our understanding of Sahaja Yoga.

00:19:07.833 --> 00:19:11.107
But for a normal person it is only electromagnetic.

00:19:11.107 --> 00:19:17.507
Now supposing a matter, which is, say,
just a matter, say a dead matter, it is.

00:19:17.507 --> 00:19:20.877
Now it is not aware that it has
got vibrations to begin with.

00:19:20.877 --> 00:19:22.557
It is not aware.

