So, but there are vibrations, there are
electromagnetic vibrations, but it is not aware.

00:19:32.717 --> 00:19:38.691
Now supposing such a dead matter, if you tell that dead matter that you have vibrations it will say, “What are you talking about?

00:19:38.699 --> 00:19:41.999
I have never felt!” But
somebody else can feel it,

00:19:41.999 --> 00:19:49.204
that there are electromagnetic vibrations. In the same way every human being has got these vibrations within him in the Spirit.

00:19:49.202 --> 00:19:53.584
But they are only manifested
when he gets Realisation.

00:19:53.655 --> 00:20:01.295
So, the second category of the same thing, the same vibrations, start expressing higher and higher qualities about it.

