Like from one seed a tree grows and the flowers come out, and they give fragrance: like that the growth is more and more.

00:20:10.375 --> 00:20:15.975
But the basic is electromagnetic
vibrations that you can feel it everywhere

00:20:16.001 --> 00:20:19.445
in the matter with your naked
eyes, a human being can see it.

00:20:19.445 --> 00:20:25.225
Now see your own growth. Have you recognised it that animals don’t know that there are electromagnetic vibrations,

00:20:25.225 --> 00:20:28.245
but human beings have?

00:20:28.284 --> 00:20:38.318
But a Sahaja Yogi knows that there are not only electromagnetic but there are all kinds of manifestations of these vibrations.

00:20:38.318 --> 00:20:44.668
So electromagnetic are important at a point and then other vibrations are even much more important.

00:20:44.688 --> 00:20:53.408
So all these vibrations are coming, combined together, absolutely completely, in a human being, which they manifest gradually.

00:20:53.472 --> 00:20:57.932
And they act according
to the need of the time.

00:20:57.932 --> 00:21:03.402
So much so that in these vibrations
there is somebody who thinks,

00:21:03.402 --> 00:21:05.902
the vibrations who think,

00:21:05.902 --> 00:21:08.072
the vibrations who cooperate,

00:21:08.072 --> 00:21:11.312
who cure,

00:21:11.346 --> 00:21:14.232
who relay things, who report things.

