sitting down here you can say show some things that are happening in India or something like that.

00:21:27.614 --> 00:21:34.356
In the same way these vibrations can report things to you. The complete telecommunication is built in these vibrations!

00:21:34.356 --> 00:21:38.016
Then you can cure people
sitting down here.

