00:22:16.714 --> 00:22:19.118
and we put them near
the head of the patient

00:22:19.139 --> 00:22:24.158
and they suck the negativity of the
person and the person gives up drinking.

00:22:24.169 --> 00:22:27.446
You have seen one boy who used
to come here, a little boy,

