And now he’s a sensible boy.
He’s started going to school.

00:22:36.952 --> 00:22:39.452
He never used to utter even a
word, now he’s started speaking.

00:22:39.472 --> 00:22:41.894
So all these things happened with the lime?

00:22:41.894 --> 00:22:45.840
Now he said, “How is it, Mother,
a lime is such a thing now?”

