are the very ultra-modern things.

00:23:05.504 --> 00:23:07.967
Because you vibrate the ultra-modern limes

00:23:07.975 --> 00:23:13.187
by your vibrations, and you
put them under the pillow.

00:23:13.184 --> 00:23:15.514
Now these limes have a speciality.

00:23:15.514 --> 00:23:18.714
And this have been found out by
many people long time back:

00:23:18.714 --> 00:23:22.934
that they have a speciality to suck in the vibrations and contain the vibrations

00:23:22.939 --> 00:23:25.695
or to, not only electromagnetic,

00:23:25.712 --> 00:23:30.365
but quite a lot of vibrations can be in it, because
