Brahmagranthi he says, because the Brahma
is the vibrating force, Brahma is Om.

00:26:25.066 --> 00:26:26.379
That is the vibrating force,

00:26:26.379 --> 00:26:34.599
because it’s the vibrations, that’s
why he calls it as the Brahmagranthi.

00:26:34.606 --> 00:26:40.021
Now the second one is the one by which
we think that we can do something.

00:26:40.071 --> 00:26:46.171
Now this one is the superego one, the first one I told you about: creates the superego, this granthi, the knot, you see..

00:26:46.191 --> 00:26:48.451
How do you have a knot?

00:26:48.461 --> 00:26:51.971
I’ll give you an example of a
balloon, say, for example, a balloon.

00:26:51.971 --> 00:26:54.482
Now a balloon has lots of air in it,

00:26:54.482 --> 00:26:59.882
but it will all pass out, it won’t be
there, if there is no knot there, you see.

00:26:59.901 --> 00:27:03.136
But if there is a knot you can hold the balloon all right.

00:27:03.136 --> 00:27:06.411
And this is the balloon we have in
our head which we call as superego,

00:27:06.421 --> 00:27:10.551
which we can see here
clearly. Can you show them?

00:27:10.551 --> 00:27:13.863
The black one, you know. The
black, real one, is this one:

00:27:13.863 --> 00:27:20.471
is the superego by which you get possessed, and
you get all mad and you do all kinds of things.

00:27:20.503 --> 00:27:23.003
This is the Brahmagranthi. This knot is there.

00:27:23.003 --> 00:27:29.483
And this knot, you see, first
starts at the Mooladhara. Now...

00:27:29.536 --> 00:27:34.433
It starts from there. The knot starts from
there, can you imagine! It starts from there!

00:27:34.480 --> 00:27:39.889
Because this one is made of prithvi-tattwa,
is made of the earth element,

00:27:39.922 --> 00:27:45.289
so from the very beginning from the
earth element itself, the knot starts.

00:27:47.534 --> 00:27:53.734
But as there is a knot: you see, when you make
a knot always there is an unwinding, always.

00:27:53.766 --> 00:27:56.644
You come by a staircase
you always can go down it.

00:27:56.676 --> 00:28:02.004
Is there a staircase by which you
cannot go down but only come up?

00:28:02.038 --> 00:28:06.796
In the same way, if you have made a knot,
there must be a way of going out of the knot.

00:28:07.938 --> 00:28:11.756
So the going out of the knot is
worked out through Sahaj Yoga.

00:28:11.756 --> 00:28:14.396
That also is done through vibrations.

00:28:14.439 --> 00:28:17.256
That the first, this
knot, has to be released.

00:28:17.274 --> 00:28:21.516
Once this knot is released
then only the Kundalini starts.

00:28:21.551 --> 00:28:25.979
This is the first knot. This
is much more important.

00:28:25.979 --> 00:28:34.819
So this first knot is very strong among
Indians and is not so strong with you people.

00:28:34.870 --> 00:28:36.762
Though in a way you have
done one great harm

